  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "innerHtml": "The place was beautiful, and the Tartar dismounted to refresh\nhimself at the fountain, but without taking off his helmet, or\nlaying aside any of his armor. Orlando was quickly at his back,\ncrying out, \"So bold, and yet a fugitive! How could you fly from a\nsingle arm and think to escape?\""
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
