  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "innerHtml": "No obstacle now stood in the way of the lovers and their faithful\nfollower in returning to France. They sailed, taking Rome in their\nway, where the Holy Father himself blessed the union of his\nnephew, Duke Huon of Bordeaux, with the Princess Clarimunda."
